quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  40,69,"Ashe, ba ka gani ba ga waɗanda ke jãyayya a cikin ãyõyin Allah, yadda ake karkatar da su"
  40,70,"Waɗanda suka ƙaryata, game da Littãfin, kuma da abin da Muka aika Manzanninmu da shi. To, za su sani"
  40,71,"A lõkacin da ƙuƙumma suke a cikin wuyõyinsu, da sarƙõƙi anã jan su"
  40,72,"A cikin ruwan zãfi, sa'an nan a cikin wutã anã babbaka su"
  40,73,"Sa'an nan a ce musu, \"Ina abin da kuka kasance kunã shirki da shi"
  40,74,"Wanin Allah?\" Suka ce: \"Sun ɓace mana. Ã'a, ba mu kasance munã kiran kõme ba a gabani.\"Kamar wancan ne Allah Yake ɓatar da kãfirai"
  40,75,"Wancan dõmin abin da kuka kasance ne kunã farin ciki da shi, a cikin ƙasã, bã da hakki ba, kuma da abin da kuka kasance kunã yi na nishãɗi"
  40,76,"Ku shiga kofõfin Jahannama kunã madawwama a cikinta. To, mazaunin mãsu girman kai yã mũnana"
  40,77,"Sabõda haka ka yi haƙuri. Lalle wa'adin Allah gaskiya ne. To, kõ dai lalle Mu nũna maka sãshen abin da Muka yi musu wa'adi da shi kõ kuwa lalle Mu karɓi ranka, to, zuwa gare Mu ake mayar da su"
  40,78,"Kuma lalle haƙĩƙa, Mun aika wasu Manzanni daga gabãninka, daga cikinsu akwai wanda Muka ƙissanta maka lãbãrinsa kuma daga cikinsu akwai wanda ba Mu ƙissanta lãbãrinsa ba a gare ka. Bã ya yiwuwa ga wani Manzo ya jẽ da wata ãyar mu'ujiza fãce da iznin Allah. Sa'an nan idan umurnin Allah ya jẽ, sai a yi hukunci da gaskiya, mãsu ɓãtãwa sun yi hasara a can"